ime.” Ondrick somberly licked his lips, put down his glass, and came over. With fat fingers, the prince undid Ondrik’s fly, extracted the entire pink mass of his private parts, selected the chief one, and started to rub regularly its glossy shaft.

“At first,” related K, “I thought that I had lost my mind, that I was hallucinating.” Most of all he was shocked by the natural quality of the procedure. Nausea welled within him, and he left. Once in the street, he even ran for a while.

